{"about_the_game":"&quot;Looped&quot; is a short interactive story. You will help Him and Her to progress by solving mini-puzzles and guiding them through the chapters. It's a peaceful story about love that's perfect to enjoy when you need a break and solve rocket puzzles.<br><br>The story will take you through time travel, but it's mostly about love. Love at first sight and love so strong it creates a wormhole in time. We get to follow Him and Her from the end to the beginning and back again, and we must help them with some minor tasks along the way. It\u2019s quirky, a dash of fun, and lots of love.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/HoldingHands.gif?t=1714495107\" /><br>One day a black hole all of a sudden appears in a young woman\u2019s living room. Out comes an unconscious man. When he finally opens his eyes, it\u2019s love at first sight. But is it the first time they see each other?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/White_Line_Width616.gif?t=1714495107\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/Rocket_Puzzle_616x384.gif?t=1714495107\" /><br><br>\u201cLooped\u201d is based on the award-winning short movie of the same name. The movie is in turn based on a short story appearing in the book \u201cOuvertyr och andra sagor f\u00f6r n\u00e4stan vuxna\u201d written by Thomas Costa Fret\u00e9 in 2022.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/White_Line_Width616.gif?t=1714495107\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/EatingCake.gif?t=1714495107\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926330/extras/White_Line_Wi